Heeeeey you did some great first steps by taking care of the trackpad and shake mouse pointer options!
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 

Those freezes might also have something to do with the Hot Corners. Take some time to try [**disabling that feature**](http://osxdaily.com/2016/08/10/disable-hot-corners-mac/) and let me know if that helps!
